Global Poly Coated Paperboard Market Insights
Poly Coated Paperboard Market size was valued at USD 15.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 22.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.9% from 2024 to 2030.

Poly Coated Paperboard Market Overview
The global poly coated paperboard market size was valued at USD 15.48 billion in 2024 and is projected to reach USD 22.84 billion by 2032, growing at a CAGR of 5.3% during the forecast period. This growth is attributed to the increasing demand for packaging solutions in industries such as food and beverages, pharmaceuticals, and consumer goods. The market's expansion is also driven by the rising trend of sustainable and eco-friendly packaging options. Poly coated paperboard is widely used due to its durability, moisture resistance, and versatile printing surface, making it a preferred choice for various applications.

